des:
Amazon Alexa and MPE Smart Control products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. After connecting Alexa to your MPE Smart Control products in a few simple steps: 
(1). Download our "MPE Smart Control" app in android or ios app market; 
(2). Register one mpe account in our " MPE Smart Control " app;
 (3). You need to have some MPE Smart Control devices in hand; 
(4). Configure these devices in our " MPE Smart Control " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in " MPE Smart Control " skills; 
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market; 
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app; 
(7). Search " MPE Smart Control " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category; 
(8). Click Enable skill of " MPE Smart Control ", and you'll be navigated to mpe login page; 
(9). Input your mpe account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page; 
(10). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these: 
“Alexa,discover my devices.” 
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
 “Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
 “Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
 “Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
 “Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.” 
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green." 
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
